{"tid":1119840,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人去過巴黎地下墓穴?","createTime":"2019-04-22T08:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T03:42:12.000Z","uid":11089,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b7c36bf50bded75cf021785bf451fcd5a701fc9","tid":1119840,"uid":11089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"1786年歐洲一度飽受瘟疫、黑死病殘害，又因為革命、戰爭有大量傷亡，死亡人數攀升到教堂放不下，導致墓地不足及環境衛生的問題，對當時抑止瘟疫極為不利，屍骨來不及腐爛卻又有&rdquo;新住民&rdquo;在外面排隊等著埋葬，最終才決定一批一批的將屍骨分類遷移地下，最終演變成公墓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fb4tVds.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFb4tVds.jpg&h=4ce4fb54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實上次我入去參觀, 初初行入展覽版區都無咩特別,<br />\n係一踏入有人骨區, feel到有陣寒氣由腳底傳去頭頂,<br />\n寒到唔敢影相 (上面張圖係google)<br />\n其實入面係咪有冷氣, 保存d人骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地有冇呢種感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e91bd7e0ff6e53fa73e9f3f44e6cb6ff6042c33","tid":1119840,"uid":92005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:06:08.000Z","msg":"有少少 成個人突然變到好depress<br />\n睇完要坐低冷靜下<br />\n行集中營都冇咁勁"},{"pid":"1fc1de7b57713e2a31b52e4bdebb29a7771cb40c","tid":1119840,"uid":95237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"LM 6月諗住去"},{"pid":"39a922f145532a4715b63c9c6b7888ff6d4972ab","tid":1119840,"uid":92005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1fc1de7b57713e2a31b52e4bdebb29a7771cb40c","tid":1119840,"uid":95237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"LM 6月諗住去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"記得早啲去 <br />\n排隊排到痴左線"},{"pid":"848817930a328b59f6d40e1eb0f67856103c81fe","tid":1119840,"uid":11089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e91bd7e0ff6e53fa73e9f3f44e6cb6ff6042c33","tid":1119840,"uid":92005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:06:08.000Z","msg":"有少少 成個人突